Chill Ray	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:GhostRaceTrait.GhostSpecialAttack.SpecialAttack.Supernatural	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:Up to twelve times per day, the ghost can attack with a ray of cold light. The ray affects a single creature within 90 feet; the ghost must make a ranged touch attack for the ray. The ray deals 2d6 points of temporary Constitution damage. In addition, the target must make a Will save (DC %1) or be affected as if by a slow spell for 1 round per each of the ghost's Hit Dice.|ChillRayDC	KEY:Ghost ~ Chill Ray				DEFINE:ChillrayDC|0					BONUS:VAR|ChillrayDC|GhostAbilityDC	BONUS:VAR|ChillrayDC|2|PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=FEAT,Ability Focus (Chill Ray)								ABILITY:Ability Focus|AUTOMATIC|Chill Ray									SOURCEPAGE:MCMoF
Deathsong	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:GhostRaceTrait.GhostSpecialAttack.SpecialAttack.Supernatural	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:Once per day, the ghost can sing a hollow dirge for 1 to 4 rounds (at the ghost's discretion). The song causes all living beings within 90 feet to become panicked unless they make a successful Will save (DC %1). Panicked creatures have a -2 morale penalty on saving throws, flee at top speed for 10 rounds, and have a 50%% chance to drop what they're holding. The song also creates a 10-foot-radius field that cancels all enchantment effects for the duration of the song plus 6 rounds afterward. Any physical attack made by the ghost while singing a deathsong deals triple normal damage.|DeathsongDC	KEY:Ghost ~ Deathsong				DEFINE:DeathsongDC|0					BONUS:VAR|DeathsongDC|GhostAbilityDC	BONUS:VAR|DeathsongDC|2|PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=FEAT,Ability Focus (Deathsong)								ABILITY:Ability Focus|AUTOMATIC|Deathsong									SOURCEPAGE:MCMoF
Energy Drain	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:GhostRaceTrait.GhostSpecialAttack.SpecialAttack.Supernatural	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:Some ghosts drain life energy, just like other undead such as vampires or wraiths. With a successful touch attack, the ghost bestows one or two negative levels (depending on the individual ghost).	KEY:Ghost ~ Energy Drain				DEFINE:EnergyDrainDC|0					BONUS:VAR|EnergyDrainDC|GhostAbilityDC	BONUS:VAR|EnergyDrainDC|2|PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=FEAT,Ability Focus (Energy Drain)								ABILITY:Ability Focus|AUTOMATIC|Energy Drain									SOURCEPAGE:MCMoF
Hit Point Drain	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:GhostRaceTrait.GhostSpecialAttack.SpecialAttack.Supernatural	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:The ghost's touch drains the hit points of its victim at a rate of 1d8 per strike. The loss of these hit points is permanent for the target of the ghost's vengeance (its killer or killers), while all others regain lost hit points as normal.	KEY:Ghost ~ Hit Point Drain																											SOURCEPAGE:MCMoF
Withering	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:GhostRaceTrait.GhostSpecialAttack.SpecialAttack.Supernatural	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:The ghost's touch acts as a rod of withering, dealing 1d4 points of temporary Strength damage and 1d4 points of temporary Constitution damage with a successful touch attack. If the ghost scores a critical hit, the damage is actually permanent ability drain instead. A Fortitude save negates the effect (DC %1).|WitheringDC	KEY:Ghost ~ Withering				DEFINE:WitheringDC|0					BONUS:VAR|WitheringDC|GhostAbilityDC	BONUS:VAR|WitheringDC|2|PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=FEAT,Ability Focus (Withering)								ABILITY:Ability Focus|AUTOMATIC|Withering									SOURCEPAGE:MCMoF
